# feat-038 Phase 5 — fixtures are read-only inputs. The synthesizer's
# emitted output lands at <fixture>/apps/web/e2e/synthesized/ when the
# script is invoked directly against the fixture (e.g. operator
# inspecting the raw output for debugging). Tests run the synthesizer
# in a temp copy so this dir doesn't grow during CI; this gitignore
# keeps any local-only operator runs out of commits.
**/apps/
